        "id": 5255
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-05-19T20:44:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In the case of only one frame, we don\u0027t put any information in fFrameHolder. We *could*, but we\u0027d have to make up values for e.g. duration, disposal method. (Maybe that\u0027s okay, and we\u0027d just use the default.)",
